subject: Snowboarding
Women
Olympic Games (2006)
lead_paragraph: After years as the only girl in a halfpipe or the only girl missing the school dance for a competition, Hannah Teter is in the spotlight. (Producers: Kassie Bracken and Shayla Harris)
